# SaaS Development Context
- **Framework**: Next.js (App Router)
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Database**: Prisma + PostgreSQL
- **Auth**: Clerk
- **Payments**: Stripe

# Builder Kit Guidelines
- When generating landing page components, use high-converting patterns (PAS framework).
- Prioritize visual excellence and rich aesthetics (glassmorphism, vibrant gradients).
- Ensure all database schemas include multi-tenant support (Organization models).
- Use Lucide React for icons.
